graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.30+]
    KubeRay -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.22.1]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x]
    KubeRay -.->|advanced routing| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1/v1beta1]
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API v1]
    KubeRay -.->|monitoring| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS HA| Redis[External Redis]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KubeRay -.->|displays status| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    KubeRay -.->|training integration| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    KubeRay -.->|pipeline execution| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines]

    %% External Services
    KubeRay -->|API management| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    KubeRay -->|image pulls| ContainerRegistry[Container Registry]
    KubeRay -.->|data storage| S3[S3/GCS Object Storage]

    %% Managed Resources
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayCluster[Ray Clusters<br/>Head + Workers]
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayJob[Ray Batch Jobs]
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayService[Ray Serve<br/>Model Serving]

    %% Integration Points
    CertManager -->|provisions| TLSCerts[TLS Certificates<br/>mTLS, Webhooks]
    TLSCerts -->|secures| RayCluster
    GatewayAPI -->|routes to| RayService
    OpenshiftRoute -->|routes to| RayService
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| KubeRay
    Prometheus -->|monitors| RayCluster

    %% Data flows
    RayCluster -->|stores state| Redis
    RayCluster -->|reads/writes| S3
    Dashboard -->|watches| RayCluster
    ModelRegistry -->|submits| RayJob
    DSPipelines -->|submits| RayJob

